# 🚀 EduMind AI — Enterprise AI Education SaaS Platform

EduMind AI is an enterprise-grade AI-powered education platform that combines:

- Conversational AI
- RAG (Retrieval-Augmented Generation)
- Voice Learning
- Personalized Study Planning
- AI Quiz Generation
- LMS Architecture
- Learning Analytics
- Enterprise Authentication

Built using:
- Python
- Streamlit
- Ollama
- Phi3
- FAISS
- NLP
- Plotly

---

# 🎯 Features

# 🤖 AI Tutor Chatbot
- Conversational AI tutor
- Personalized learning assistance
- Context-aware responses
- Multi-turn conversations

---

# 📄 AI Notes Analyzer
- Upload PDFs/Notes
- OCR-ready architecture
- Semantic search
- Educational RAG pipeline
- AI-powered summarization

---

# 📝 AI Quiz Generator
- AI-generated MCQs
- Difficulty-based quizzes
- Automatic evaluation
- Score tracking
- Smart assessments

---

# 📊 Learning Analytics
- Quiz performance tracking
- AI learning insights
- Progress dashboards
- Achievement system
- Personalized recommendations

---

# 🧠 Personalized AI Study Planner
- AI-generated study schedules
- Adaptive learning roadmap
- Weak-topic detection
- Productivity optimization

---

# 🎤 Voice Learning Assistant
- Speech-to-text learning
- Voice-based AI tutor
- Interactive learning assistant

---

# 👨‍🏫 Teacher Dashboard
- Course management
- Student monitoring
