# 🧠 Tech Stack

| Category | Technologies |
|---|---|
| Frontend | Streamlit, Plotly |
| Backend | Python, SQLite |
| AI/GenAI | Ollama, Phi3 |
| NLP | Sentence Transformers |
| Vector DB | FAISS |
| Authentication | bcrypt |
| Voice AI | SpeechRecognition |

