          │
          ▼
EduMind AI Platform
          │
 ┌────────┼────────┐
 ▼        ▼        ▼
AI Tutor  RAG      Analytics
          │
          ▼
FAISS Vector Database
          │
          ▼
Phi3 AI Model
          │
          ▼
Personalized Learning
```

